Program: Outlook
Title: Sorious Samura Filming Illegal Immigration
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrw5
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Interview with journalist Sorious Samura whose programme 'Living With Illegals' deals with illegal immigration from Africa into Europe. Also, watching the Mines Advisory Group in action clearing landmines in Cambodia and mine-clearing in Cyprus; veterans of 'Pingpong Diplomacy' revisit China; diamond polishing in Surat. Show less